No. 09-1397 (R46-030). Shirley M. Lewis, et al., Petitioners v. National Labor Relations Board, et al. 561 U.S. 1055, 131 S. Ct. 59,

177 L. Ed. 2d 1148,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 5734. September 16, 2010.

The petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Fourth Circuit in the above-entitled case was dismissed today pursuant to Rule 46 of the Rules of this Court.

Same case below, 587 F.3d 654.
